{"tid":1895401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★行山？坪洲居民困擾　店主：有遊客不戴口罩狂咳兼搶購廁紙！","createTime":"2020-02-24T13:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T05:26:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2d7776361e9d6ac6424ad5d432bf9f08795102","tid":1895401,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"「香港人嚟離島玩，唔支持小店唔緊要，但可否珍惜我哋居民呢處叫家的地方？」在坪洲開小店的「Cinpou」店主在facebook發帖，表示昨日全坪洲塞滿人，其店舖生意沒多少帶動，「連一張十蚊明信片都冇人幫襯」。店主指明白大家都有經濟壓力，沒幫襯不要緊，但最不滿是有香港遊客遊玩後，還要在島上搶購廁紙，「搶到要call車去中環碼頭接你」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4052503/org/0aced5e97e4023db674727666ad69c64.jpg/R4KI_ZgFFhvqo-mlbaymYqmTF_H_MQy3VNtMjVTbTI0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4052503%2Forg%2F0aced5e97e4023db674727666ad69c64.jpg%2FR4KI_ZgFFhvqo-mlbaymYqmTF_H_MQy3VNtMjVTbTI0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=29562e48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n店主又抱怨有遊客<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不戴口罩</strong></span>走入店內，突然狂咳還怪店主點香令他鼻敏感，店主待這缺德客離開後，還要消毒整間舖，「一邊抹一邊流眼淚，很無奈」。<br />\n<br />\n有相信同樣居於坪洲的網民留言，指遊客湧到島上令人煩擾，批評遊客早上10時許就在其家門外嘈吵，四處跑又不戴口罩，賞花時又動手動腳；為怕感染，屋主只好每日都用漂白水洗地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/438936/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E9%80%BC%E7%88%86%E5%9D%AA%E6%B4%B2%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%9B%B0%E6%93%BE-%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%BB-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%A8%E8%B5%B0%E4%BB%B2%E6%90%B6%E8%B3%BC%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F438936%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2580%25BC%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%259D%25AA%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%2593%25BE-%25E5%25BA%2597%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2587%25A8%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E6%2590%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25BB%2581%25E7%25B4%2599&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=ffdc50b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/438936/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E9%80%BC%E7%88%86%E5%9D%AA%E6%B4%B2%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%9B%B0%E6%93%BE-%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%BB-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%A8%E8%B5%B0%E4%BB%B2%E6%90%B6%E8%B3%BC%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99</a>"},{"pid":"f3d2b3af2be4c23e42b1e887137829c5639daa5c","tid":1895401,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:39:28.000Z","msg":"坪洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcac91c6ad99039d77ee4fac7db6bd308165c51","tid":1895401,"uid":275885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"入到坪洲搶廁紙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWtf 咩人黎"},{"pid":"e03f3127048f11eeb15592781faf933109d00b01","tid":1895401,"uid":87576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲"},{"pid":"ba6e4a42d090ae95ee336b519334b81f26105e15","tid":1895401,"uid":228437,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:51:59.000Z","msg":"入島買廁紙真係賤格喎"},{"pid":"17be58ae23bda7e5c7b8d0a2235ce94acebb51ea","tid":1895401,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:15:22.000Z","msg":"銀礦灣多唔多人住酒店？"},{"pid":"5d67d020f820eee74226a7d47d75379a7376568d","tid":1895401,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"保家護國,驅逐港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />